  // Gen 0: ##. / #.. / ...  => cells [(0,0),(1,0),(0,1)]
  // Dead cell (1,1) has 3 live neighbors -> becomes alive
  // Gen 1: ##. / ##. / ... => cells [(0,0),(1,0),(0,1),(1,1)]
